WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.980 --> 00:00:03.040
Have you seen this man?

2
00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:06.379
Yes, I've seen him.

3
00:00:06.379 --> 00:00:08.609
I need to know what room he's in.

4
00:00:08.609 --> 00:00:10.609
I need the key. Now, please, it's urgent.

5
00:00:10.609 --> 00:00:13.609
I'm sorry we can't disclose guest information.

6
00:00:13.609 --> 00:00:19.780
The man in this photo is my husband.

7
00:00:19.780 --> 00:00:21.780
And the woman he's with is a mistress.

8
00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:23.780
If you don't give me the room key now,

9
00:00:23.780 --> 00:00:30.160
you'll be covering up an affair.

10
00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:33.159
All right, I despise cheating men.

11
00:00:33.159 --> 00:00:37.299
All right, here's the room key, presidential sweep.

12
00:00:37.299 --> 00:00:39.299
Go, go catch him in the act.

13
00:00:39.299 --> 00:00:41.299
Make sure you teach Melissa.

14
00:00:41.299 --> 00:00:42.299
Thank you.

15
00:00:42.299 --> 00:01:01.299
I'm at the Paradise Hotel.

16
00:01:01.299 --> 00:01:04.299
Jessie and Miles are in her room and I really need some help, please.

17
00:01:04.299 --> 00:01:05.390
What?

18
00:01:05.390 --> 00:01:07.390
Elaine, don't cry. I'm on my way.

